data: Awarded by Escorts Kubota Limited for top supplier for 24 years. Apr 9, 2023 Pranjal Projects Pvt. Ltd. was recognized as the top supplier for the 24th consecutive year by Escorts Kubota Limited in April 2023. This accolade is a testament to our long-standing partnership, built on mutual trust, quality, and consistent delivery of high-performance products. Over the years, we have supplied a range of precision-engineered components that meet the exacting standards of Escorts. Our shared commitment to innovation and quality has strengthened this relationship, positioning Pranjal Projects as a reliable partner in the construction and infrastructure equipment industry. We look forward to continuing this partnership and building on our success in the years to come. Request a Quote
